flowchart LR
  %% Pricing Engine Pipeline (Explainable)
  IN[Inputs\n- neighborhood\n- date & nights\n- min/max guardrails\n- property description] --> MD["Market Data Fetch\n(listings + metrics)"]
  IN --> SIM["Similar Listings\n(embeddings / comps)"]
  MD --> BASE[Base Price Anchor]
  SIM --> BASE

  BASE --> SIG[Pricing Signals\n- occupancy\n- lead time\n- competitor pressure\n- length of stay\n- last-minute surge]
  SIG --> AGG["Aggregation\n(weighted adjustments)"]
  AGG --> CLAMP["Guardrail Clamp\n(min/max + sanity checks)"]
  CLAMP --> OUT[Outputs\n- recommended price\n- signal breakdown\n- confidence/risk band\n- 7-day forecast]
